94
00:04:38,679 --> 00:04:40,399
Kita berada di atas kapal yang sama.

95
00:04:40,679 --> 00:04:42,480
Kau maupun kami takkan bisa kabur.

96
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,239
Kami sudah mengeluarkan miliaran dana.

97
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,480
