227
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,599
di dalam penjara, 'kan?

228
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:09,559
Apa kau tahu kenapa sampai sekarang
kau masih jomblo?

229
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,719
Kau tak tahu cara menikmati hidup.

230
00:11:14,239 --> 00:11:15,599
